# Unreal binary content lives in Git LFS (CLAUDE.md §Repo conventions).
# Extend during week 0 first-commit hygiene if the generated project adds
# other large binary types (.ubulk, source art, etc.).
# Note: *_BuiltData.uasset is .gitignore'd, so it never reaches the index or
# LFS despite matching the pattern below — that absence is intentional.
*.uasset filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.umap filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
